"title": "8713: discouragement",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8713",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sense of unhappiness arising from a loss of confidence in one's own abilities, in the reliability of God or in the power of the gospel. Discouragement can occur in the Christian life, especially when there is resistance to the gospel or in instances of personal failure. Scripture provides reassurance for those who experience discouragement.</p>\n<h2>The experience of discouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:20-Job3:26\">JOB 3:20–3:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:4-Num21:5\">NUM 21:4–21:5</a> <em>the Israelites in the desert</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:8-Josh2:11\">JOS 2:8–2:11</a> <em>the Canaanites and Rahab</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:10-1Sam17:11\">1SA 17:10–17:11</a> <em>the Israelites and Goliath</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:26\">2KI 19:26</a> <em>God's judgment on Sennacherib</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:6-Job5:7\">JOB 5:6–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:1-Ps38:14\">PSA 38:1–38:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:26-Prov1:27\">PRO 1:26–1:27</a> <em>Wisdom speaks to the sinner</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17-Eccl2:20\">ECC 2:17–2:20</a> <em>the Teacher's disillusion</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:2-Isa21:4\">ISA 21:2–21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer45:3\">JER 45:3</a> <em>to Baruch</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:7\">EZK 21:7</a> <em>God's judgment on Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8-2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:8–1:9</a> <em>Paul</em></p>\n<h2>Prayer in discouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5-Ps42:11\">PSA 42:5–42:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:6-Deut26:7\">DEU 26:6–26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:7\">2SA 22:7</a> <em>David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:9\">2CH 20:9</a> <em>Jehoshaphat</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:32\">NEH 9:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:12\">PSA 31:9–31:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:14\">ISA 38:14</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:18-Jer8:19\">JER 8:18–8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:1-Jonah2:2\">JON 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Endurance in discouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:3-Isa42:4\">ISA 42:3–42:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:4-2Cor6:10\">2CO 6:4–6:10</a> <em>Paul</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2TH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:32\">HEB 10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:3\">HEB 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:3\">REV 2:3</a> <em>concerning the church at Ephesus</em></p>\n<h2>Discouragement through disobedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:9\">JER 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:15-1Sam28:18\">1SA 28:15–28:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:24-Job15:25\">JOB 15:24–15:25</a> <em>Eliphaz to Job</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:17\">ZEP 1:17</a></p>\n<h2>Discouragement and discipline</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:7\">HEB 12:5–12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:14-Judg2:15\">JDG 2:14–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:16\">ISA 26:16</a></p>\n<h2>Effects of discouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:22\">PRO 17:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:9\">EXO 6:9</a> <em>the Israelites in Egypt</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:1\">2SA 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:4\">EZR 4:4</a> <em>the rebuilding of the temple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:5\">JOB 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:13\">PRO 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:14\">PRO 18:14</a></p>\n<h2>Resisting discouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:21\">DEU 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">JOS 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:1\">JOS 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:32\">1SA 17:32</a> <em>David reassuring Saul about Goliath</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:13\">1CH 22:13</a> <em>David to Solomon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:7\">2CH 32:7</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:46\">JER 51:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:1\">LUK 18:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:9\">GAL 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:13\">EPH 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:5\">2TI 4:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's help in discouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:6\">DEU 31:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:8\">DEU 31:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:23\">DEU 31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">JOS 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:20\">1CH 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:15\">2CH 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:17\">2CH 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:18\">PSA 34:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:29-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:29–40:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10\">JER 30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:6\">2CO 7:6</a> <em>Paul</em></p>\n<h2>Warnings not to discourage others</h2>\n<h3>The Israelites discouraged when on the point of entering the promised land</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:12\">OBA 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:28\">DEU 1:28</a> <em>by the spies</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:7\">NUM 32:7</a> <em>by the Gadites and Reubenites</em></p>\n<h3>General warnings not to discourage others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:16\">PSA 109:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19\">ACT 15:19</a> <em>James advises against discouraging the Gentiles</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:21\">COL 3:21</a></p>\n<h2>The need to stand with the discouraged</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:3\">HEB 13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:14\">JOB 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:21\">JER 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>",
